  "texts": [
    "We aimed to obtain 20 ratings per reappraisal as our analysis suggested that it would be sufficient to obtain a similar precision as our first study (see Supplemental Materials).",
    "As such, we",
    "recruited a new set of raters who completed an identical reappraisal training and rating process as the raters in Study 1's rating task.",
    "These raters rated 50 reappraisals each in terms of effectiveness, empathy, novelty, and specificity.",
    "1077 raters completed the task."
  ],
